    dc:description "Fig. 16. Campylocera loewi: holotype ♀ Hypotyphlina saegeri (MRAC): 1 — habitus, dorsal view; 2 — wing; 3 — head, left; 4 — mesonotum; 5 — abdomen, left; 6 — labels." ;
